import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import React from 'react'
import './index.css'
import ButtonAppBar from './AppBar'
import TemporaryDrawer from './TemporaryDrawer.js'

ReactDOM.render(
    [
        <ButtonAppBar />,
        <TemporaryDrawer />
    ],
    document.getElementById('root')
);
